UUID.name: UUID
UUID.description: Universally Unique Identifier information. The syntax must conform to RFC 4122, Section 4.1.

UUIDorZero.name: UUIDorZero
UUIDorZero.description: Universally Unique Identifier information. The syntax must conform to RFC 4122, Section 4.1. The semantics of the value zero-length OCTET STRING are object-specific and must therefore be defined as part of the description of any object that uses this syntax.
